article.description: Kameron Langley had a career-high 22 points plus 12 assists as North Carolina A&T; topped Morgan State 76-70 on Monday night.
article.headline: Langley scores 22 to lead NC A&T over Morgan St. 76-70
article.linkText: Langley scores 22 to lead NC A&T over Morgan St. 76-70
article.story: BALTIMORE -- Kameron Langley had a career-high 22 points plus 12 assists as North Carolina A&T; topped Morgan State 76-70 on Monday night. Andre Jackson had 15 points for the Aggies (8-12, 4-1 Mid-Eastern Athletic Conference). Ronald Jackson added 12 points and 18 rebounds and Devin Haygood had three blocks. Stanley Davis had 21 points and nine rebounds for the Bears (9-12, 3-3). Troy Baxter added 14 points and five blocks and Kyson Rawls had 12 points.
